{"tid":1467480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察涉嫌毆打大陸記者，被香港示威者制止","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:45.000Z","uid":42360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10e8c62896fe9c22e942e783ee21023a60d560e1","tid":1467480,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"今日機場件事係香港警察一如早前承認，裝扮成示威者，企圖帶領群眾毆打大陸記者，幸得香港和平理性的示威者制止。最後，該名大陸記者被由示威者自發組成的急救人員救出，成功脫離香港警察魔掌。<br />\n<br />\n促請中央政府，中國記協譴責香港警察濫用暴力。"},{"pid":"6a97038e61c9e1d8508abf38f5e66d8bb68c6efe","tid":1467480,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f765e4dee1be85cb98ed854e15fa842dd559d7bf","tid":1467480,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1958f68373a0bfd843549289c12a5ea7e434f7ac","tid":1467480,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"851674263890b19242039c1e64a85d46f6932ab8","tid":1467480,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e46f7bb30f9f9df55de6689350a6658793a06aa","tid":1467480,"uid":63298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}